summary: During my first semester at college I had a depressive episode, which was very intense and confusing at the time. I was at my...
body:
During my first semester at college I had a depressive episode, which was very intense and confusing at the time. I was at my dream school with my friend since 8th grade as my roomate.

Knowing I was depressed, one day I got back from class to find she decided to surprise me by putting glowing in the dark stars everywhere.

It’s one of my favorite memories.
